{"tid":660980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解豬一定要全熟牛唔洗？","createTime":"2018-05-11T06:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T10:15:40.000Z","uid":64412,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa513cd48ecb9494e6d482be1db7d79a9fc5f33","tid":660980,"uid":64412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n希望唔好屌得咁大力"},{"pid":"56a9ce3d4f984b48bb563101bed14305b6e54efe","tid":660980,"uid":50935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cfa513cd48ecb9494e6d482be1db7d79a9fc5f33","tid":660980,"uid":64412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n希望唔好屌得咁大力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"豬有蟲？"},{"pid":"3abadb2f6beaae895f4a6db0daa59a21d224d210","tid":660980,"uid":51092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"啲豬好dirrrty 㗎"},{"pid":"fc67956ef816995039c768585350bda94c69e7d4","tid":660980,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:04:02.000Z","msg":"牛其實都有菌 但未多到令人體不適"},{"pid":"1e7daa56ab10f4ff3c24fdd0088ed92a661a380b","tid":660980,"uid":23937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"因為豬係雜食性動物，牛係草食性動物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（好似係）"},{"pid":"b28ad01604af5eacde4b12405e387d5db6bbc609","tid":660980,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"【環球薈報】日餐廳禁供應豬肝豬肉刺身<br />\n2015年5月28日 15:47<br />\n<br />\n【now新聞台】日本人喜歡吃刺身，但日本共同社報道，日本厚生勞動省下令，由下月中起，所有餐廳一律不准供應豬肝和豬肉刺身，以減低食物中毒的機會。<br />\n<br />\n厚生勞動省指豬肉和豬肝可能帶有可致命的戊型肝炎病毒，而且豬肝表面可能有沙門氏菌等惡菌，容易引致食物中毒。厚生勞動省因而決定修改食品衛生法，規定所有餐廳處理豬肝時，要以攝氏63度加熱30分鐘以上。若違例，餐廳東主可能面臨兩年以下的有期徒刑，或罰款200萬日圓，折合約12萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n早在2011年，日本曾經爆發大規模食物中毒，導致5人死亡，180人不適，病人全在同一間餐廳吃過生牛肉後發病。因此，當局在三年前收緊有關法例，禁止餐廳供應牛肝刺身。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=137527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D137527&d=mdgRpUJljFQUQVQESb%2F3fdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ff557d97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D137527&h=e5a687bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=137527</a><br />\n<br />\n自製「豬刺身」 泰兩男食到死<br />\n  3,539 views │ 2015年10月27日<br />\n泰國北部兩名男子自製「豬肉刺身」，兩人食用後即出現腹瀉、頭暈等症狀，最終受細菌感染而亡。<br />\n<br />\n北部素可泰府（Sukhothai）兩名男子，上周三買豬肉自製「涼拌生豬肉」，結果當晚就不舒服，男子家人將他們送院治療，醫院抽血檢驗後發現，兩人的血液受細菌嚴重感染，而且已經擴散到腦部，由於他們未有及時接受治療，終延至周日不治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20151027/288381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20151027%2F288381&d=mdgRpUJljFQUQVQESb%2F3fdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c0e55406\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20151027%2F288381&h=b63d64b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20151027/288381</a>"},{"pid":"1d02d2a063b7e3cab7b44738e962f550699a0aab","tid":660980,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"豬係不潔"},{"pid":"cb09d3b668bdae1e6a78019c6f9dbba784429501","tid":660980,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"因為牛全熟好un"},{"pid":"fbfda27e39a7a2080b4f5e9a747ced9658c63694","tid":660980,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"小學生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77ddd95fb778aec0b7089607158767b3e9a406a","tid":660980,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d02d2a063b7e3cab7b44738e962f550699a0aab","tid":660980,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"豬係不潔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"講起不潔既豬肉<br />\n我淨係今年，已經見過超過廿個迴去食韓燒<br />\n佢地食完韓燒入一入廁所出返黎已經戴返頭巾"},{"pid":"663d445f7900ba3acfda010229087020e3871828","tid":660980,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"因為牛係食草"},{"pid":"e03ee920a1ba9142e075393ba81dcbc8c0dc7f38","tid":660980,"uid":44187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"因為你就係嗰隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43409a049acb2fc6969e23c8723c4ed6987b5167","tid":660980,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"痴能線日本人乜柒都生食"},{"pid":"8b518fcda539143c13af96f643268c7f2c3739d0","tid":660980,"uid":117901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43409a049acb2fc6969e23c8723c4ed6987b5167","tid":660980,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"痴能線日本人乜柒都生食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"好過大陸人乜柒都食"},{"pid":"f58feabfe248f7f0ecdf21d1f2042997bf035fbf","tid":660980,"uid":97235,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"豬有寄生虫叫鉤絛蟲，食咗有鉤絛蟲蟲卵既生豬肉，就會有機會中招，寄生蟲由腸道岀世，再進入身體的各部分，包括腦、眼、肌肉"},{"pid":"601a736eadcc18d6481986112adf7a4ea2ee86dc","tid":660980,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:01:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/猪肉绦虫\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%8C%AA%E8%82%89%E7%BB%A6%E8%99%AB&d=mdgRpUJljFQUQVQESb%2F3fdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c355be79\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/猪肉绦虫</a><br />\n<br />\n經豬肉進入人體"},{"pid":"98752218b323b9bb3563cb4bb7136c6915f97d51","tid":660980,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f58feabfe248f7f0ecdf21d1f2042997bf035fbf","tid":660980,"uid":97235,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"